---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuickSummary from '../components/QuickSummary.astro';
---

<Layout title="Base Building" description="Building and research priorities from new player to mid-game in Last War: Survival.">
  <h1>Base Building</h1>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p>HQ level is king early. After that, focus buildings and research that directly increase the power of your main squad type (Troop Center, relevant Research Lab tech, Gear Workshop, etc.).</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <p>Do not upgrade every building evenly. Some buildings give almost zero return until very high levels.</p>
</Layout>